  "lastUpdatedOn": "2012-09-23",
  "religion": "Shania Twain followed the Sant Mat philosophy, which is big on meditation, with her first husband. But no news on whether or not she's still a follower.",
  "politicalViews": "She's claims to be non-political, but Democratic politicians and PETA are fans of hers.",
  "author": "Caitlin Frye",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 1
    },
    {
      "parentId": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Shania Twain, whose given name is Eilleen Regina Edwards, was born in Windsor, Ontario and raised in Timmons, Ontario, with a brief stint in Toronto."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 2
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Twain grew up Christian,",
      "sourceTitle": "For Shania Twain who practices a religion called Sant Mat.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.annointed.net/Community/prayer-salvation-someone-you-love/36524-shania-twain-who-practices-relgion-called-sant-mat.html"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "but practiced a syncretic eastern philosophy called Sant Mat with her first husband.",
      "parentId": 2,
      "sourceTitle": "Shania's Secret Side.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,386726,00.html"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "The philosophy emphasizes meditation, yoga, non-violence, and eating a vegetarian diet–among other things.",
      "parentId": 2,
      "sourceTitle": "Contemporary Sant Mat movements.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Contemporary_Sant_Mat_movements"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 3
    },
    {
      "parentId": 3,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "She kept her life very private during this time, so we don't know a whole lot about her spiritual practices. We know she's a vegetarian",
      "sourceTitle": "Celebrity Vegetarians and Vegans.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.allamericanspeakers.com/Celebrity_Vegetarians.php"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "and that she practices yoga,",
      "parentId": 3,
      "sourceTitle": "Shania Twain's 5 Steps Recovery After Cheating Spouse Breaks Her Heart.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.babble.com/cs/famecrawler/2008/12/07/shania-twain-s-5-step-recovery-after-cheating-spouse-breaks-her-heart/"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "but that's about it. Regardless of the details, she's obviously a spiritual person:",
      "parentId": 3
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 4
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 5,
      "parentId": 4
    },
    {
      "parentId": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I'm always soul searching on a spiritual level. That's a permanent occupation of mine, I think, for the rest of my life.",
      "sourceTitle": "CMT Insider Interview: Shania Twain.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.cmt.com/news/country-music/1560540/cmt-insider-interview-shania-twain.jhtml"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 6
    },
    {
      "parentId": 6,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "But Twain's been pretty pissed ever since her husband left her for her best friend, so there's at least a decent chance she ditched the philosophy with the man."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "id": 7
    },
    {
      "parentId": 7,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Politics for the non-political"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 8
    },
    {
      "parentId": 8,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Twain says she's not a political person, or at least she's tolerant of other viewpoints and wants to keep hers to herself:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 9
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 10,
      "parentId": 9
    },
    {
      "parentId": 10,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I'm not the politician, and I just completely remove myself from that. I don't have anything against or for any particular person or point of view on politics. I have my own opinions, but my songs don't share them.",
      "sourceTitle": "CMT Insider Interview: Shania Twain.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.cmt.com/news/country-music/1560540/cmt-insider-interview-shania-twain.jhtml"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 11
    },
    {
      "parentId": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "That didn't stop both Hillary Clinton and Al Gore from using her song, \"Rock This Country!\" during their campaigns.",
      "sourceTitle": "Shania Twain – Rock This Country!",
      "sourceUrl": "http://politicaltunes.wordpress.com/2012/05/10/shania-twain-rock-this-country/"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I guess they didn't care that she's a Canadian who lives in Switzerland.",
      "parentId": 11
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 12
    },
    {
      "parentId": 12,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Twain hasn't come out for or against hot political issues like gay marriage, but she did get a shout-out from PETA (People for the Ethical Treatment of Animals) for being one of their \"Sexiest Vegetarian Celebrities.\"",
      "sourceTitle": "PETA's Sexiest Vegetarian Celebrities of 2012.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://features.peta.org/sexiest-vegetarian-celebrities-2012/#Female"
    }
  ],
